al run leg but Yee came roaring back to upgrade his Tokyo silver, overhauling Wilde in the closing stages.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9841122656094419, \"rank\": 0.016144217373871887, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.999960287637375, \"rank\": 3.970876087695368e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a case of d\\u00e9j\\u00e0 vu for Wilde in Sunday's Boston supertri as Yee left it late once again to overtake and take the win.\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.999960287637375, \"rank\": 3.970876087695368e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9949587106328844, \"rank\": 0.004291512116527925, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee left this comeback even later, overtaking a tiring Wilde on the home straight and pounding his chest as he made his way to the finish line.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.999960287637375, \"rank\": 3.970876087695368e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old, who was born in Lewisham, was even able to showboat with victory in the bag, slowing down as he crossed the line with his arms folded.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewisham\", \"score\": 0.9995969024321698, \"rank\": 0.0004027093857061079, \"text\": \"Lewisham\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewisham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewisham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The celebrate irritated Wilde, who aimed angry glances at his rival and threw his arms up in the air, havingshowed great sportsmanship following their epic tussle in Paris.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.999960287637375, \"rank\": 3.970876087695368e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.8556054033839594e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ITS HAPPENED AGAIN!\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b6 Cold finish for@Lixsanyeepic.twitter.com/WDIbb6k3Kc  Some social media users criticised Yee's celebration, describing it as 'classless' and 'arrogant', but others praised the Team GB star.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999996887332174, \"rank\": 2.888232637259789e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Who would have guessed Olympic gold medalist triathlete Alex Yee was cold as ice?'\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1336, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"one said, while another added: 'Nah, this guy's a menace and I am here for it.'\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to an account on X that criticised his celebration, Yee said sarcastically: 'No celebration next time, apologies.'\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde, meanwhile, said he was desperate to get his hands on gold in next week's Chicago triathlon after being beaten by Yee yet again.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.99970115631152, \"rank\": 0.00016880758276682163, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Oh man, I think I have been seeing too many silvers in the last couple of weeks so it would be nice to get a gold so yeah, bring on Chicago,' he said.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.99970115631152, \"rank\": 0.00016880758276682163, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee followed up his Olympic gold in Paris bywinning bronze in the triathlon mixed relay alongside Georgia Taylor-Brown, Sam Dickinson and Beth Potter.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.8556054033839594e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgia Taylor-Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\", \"score\": 0.999985295493271, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Dickinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Potter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after securing gold in the individual event, Yee said: 'I am not really sure myself (how I managed it), to be honest.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was just one of those magic moments where you hear about these Olympic moments and people finding extra stuff within themselves.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was just one of those where I just decided that I was going to give myself one last chance just to do it.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'If I did that, then I gave myself a shot.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if I come 10th, that's fine.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I come last, that's fine.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I guess it went beyond my wildest dreams.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'To be able to go into this one with a little bit of expectation, admittedly, and all my friends and family around was really special, to be able to deliver that.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think it's probably one of the most beautiful venues we have ever done the triathlon and probably the Olympic Games has ever seen.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is super special.'\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:'I hope you understand' - Olympics star defects to Team GB after Paris 2024  ArrowMORE:Eddie Hearn offers to promote Imane Khelif after Olympic boxing gender row  ArrowMORE:'I lived in the Emily in Paris building - our lives are eerily similar'  Your guide to the week in football.\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999996887332174, \"rank\": 2.888232637259789e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped